<h1>Firefox extension</h1>

<p>Browser extensions are applications that run inside your web browser and provide additional functionality, integration with third party websites or services, and customized browsing experiences.</p>

<p>The Factlink extension will enable you to use Factlink on virtually all websites you visit.</p>

<p>You can install the extension from the <b class="caret" style="margin: 7px 0 0;"></b> menu in the top bar.</p>

